"smart_blocks: 想法/想法记录/题目收集.md#题目收集##解答  (1) 求夹角 $\\theta$ 椭圆 $\\Gamma: \\frac{x^2}{3}+y^2=1$，点 $A$ 的横坐标为 $-\\frac{3}{2}$，代入椭圆方程得： $$\\frac{(-\\frac{3}{2})^2}{3} + y^2 = 1 \\implies \\frac{3}{4} + y^2 = 1 \\implies y = \\pm \\frac{1}{2}$$ 直线 $l_1$ 过 $M(0,2)$ 和 $A$，设 $l_1$ 的斜率为 $k_1$，直线与椭圆交于相异两点，故判别式 $\\Delta>0$： 联立 $y=kx+2$ 与椭圆方程，得 $\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)x^2+4kx+3=0$，$\\Delta=16k^2-4\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)\\cdot3=4k^2-4>0$，即 $|k|>1$。 - 若 $y=\\frac{1}{2}$，则 $k_1=\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=1$，$\\Delta=0$（相切，舍去）； - 若 $y=-\\frac{1}{2}$，则 $k_1=\\frac{-\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=\\frac{5}{3}$，满足 $|k|>1$。 $l_1,l_2$ 关于 $y$ 轴对称，故 $l_2$ 的斜率 $k_2=-\\frac{5}{3}$。两直线夹角公式：$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{|1+k_1k_2|}{\\sqrt{1+k_1^2}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+k_2^2}}$，代入得： $$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{\\left|1-\\frac{25}{9}\\right|}{\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}}=\\frac{\\frac{16}{9}}{\\frac{34}{9}}=\\frac{8}{17}$$ 故 $\\theta=\\arccos\\frac{8}{17}$。": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06789392,-0.06311532,0.03279934,-0.03510474,-0.00782438,0.02719029,-0.00776064,-0.03450894,0.03533194,-0.0049205,0.02926736,-0.06101606,0.03862847,-0.02237917,0.03217527,-0.0044425,0.00436215,0.02402803,-0.08194665,-0.02869842,0.15614641,-0.0745247,-0.01811338,-0.05078245,0.08263489,0.06908841,-0.01784547,-0.03477907,0.02429763,-0.14670676,-0.0097606,-0.04420661,0.00689116,0.03051253,-0.02260725,-0.06691612,-0.08196934,0.02353254,-0.09802067,0.02275661,-0.00241377,0.02060257,0.06382391,-0.01891725,0.00566241,-0.0435262,-0.01061465,0.00510749,-0.04348914,-0.02530095,-0.07197572,0.06817712,0.04922289,-0.02017323,0.00042209,0.0181824,0.0306506,0.09787767,0.04467213,0.02273959,0.01098619,0.01768109,-0.166566,-0.00190471,0.04681368,0.05112427,0.03492021,-0.05220805,0.04142705,0.11474162,-0.01780521,0.01334649,-0.02607641,0.08861397,-0.02333413,-0.02792879,-0.00403453,-0.00926278,-0.05590065,-0.00729481,-0.0318572,0.03911708,-0.0083712,0.0119476,0.0109