"smart_blocks: 想法/想法记录/题目收集.md#题目收集##解答  (1) 求夹角 $\\theta$ 椭圆 $\\Gamma: \\frac{x^2}{3}+y^2=1$，点 $A$ 的横坐标为 $-\\frac{3}{2}$，代入椭圆方程得： $$\\frac{(-\\frac{3}{2})^2}{3} + y^2 = 1 \\implies \\frac{3}{4} + y^2 = 1 \\implies y = \\pm \\frac{1}{2}$$ 直线 $l_1$ 过 $M(0,2)$ 和 $A$，设 $l_1$ 的斜率为 $k_1$，直线与椭圆交于相异两点，故判别式 $\\Delta>0$： 联立 $y=kx+2$ 与椭圆方程，得 $\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)x^2+4kx+3=0$，$\\Delta=16k^2-4\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)\\cdot3=4k^2-4>0$，即 $|k|>1$。 - 若 $y=\\frac{1}{2}$，则 $k_1=\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=1$，$\\Delta=0$（相切，舍去）； - 若 $y=-\\frac{1}{2}$，则 $k_1=\\frac{-\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=\\frac{5}{3}$，满足 $|k|>1$。 $l_1,l_2$ 关于 $y$ 轴对称，故 $l_2$ 的斜率 $k_2=-\\frac{5}{3}$。两直线夹角公式：$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{|1+k_1k_2|}{\\sqrt{1+k_1^2}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+k_2^2}}$，代入得： $$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{\\left|1-\\frac{25}{9}\\right|}{\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}}=\\frac{\\frac{16}{9}}{\\frac{34}{9}}=\\frac{8}{17}$$ 故 $\\theta=\\arccos\\frac{8}{17}$。#{1}": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06601921,-0.0599579,0.03104972,-0.03441225,-0.00755286,0.02828662,-0.01013441,-0.03255976,0.03472934,-0.00600925,0.02913202,-0.06139375,0.03970499,-0.0264856,0.03355241,-0.00399544,0.00186237,0.02190507,-0.08281855,-0.02998507,0.15481453,-0.07497884,-0.018642,-0.05201444,0.08289105,0.06855769,-0.01893505,-0.03553929,0.02455943,-0.14742307,-0.00582287,-0.04856233,0.00775092,0.03052259,-0.022333,-0.06954264,-0.0816961,0.02343444,-0.09925103,0.0220244,-0.00462408,0.01987582,0.0605007,-0.02162873,0.00506093,-0.04526267,-0.0100303,0.00341425,-0.04398708,-0.02339987,-0.06826183,0.07055409,0.04810913,-0.0213772,0.00257109,0.0177973,0.02641849,0.09595759,0.04403405,0.02467833,0.01265634,0.01587181,-0.16535988,-0.00366273,0.04600041,0.0520006,0.03445901,-0.05082699,0.04203729,0.11823335,-0.01801541,0.01379058,-0.02829042,0.08936601,-0.02106034,-0.0288303,-0.00223134,-0.00736659,-0.05535311,-0.00683491,-0.03092092,0.03784639,-0.00904577,0.01275438,0.01