03379774,-0.03386988,-0.03410399,0.03084627,0.04914347,-0.01161475,0.00786949,-0.0360398,-0.0241323,-0.01755097,-0.01343443,-0.04540083,0.06323342,0.02891352,0.04023416,-0.0223482,0.02094131,0.03700503,-0.0220574,-0.09897734,-0.0081241,-0.00665273,0.02305691,-0.03890686,-0.00245538,0.0078151,0.00450603,0.0178828,0.01612955,0.00597123,-0.01299498,0.04201668,0.01631206,-0.07018473,0.10750818,0.01491993,-0.035861,0.09691982,0.01067084,-0.00288262,0.03749976,-0.01580862,-0.0183715,0.02605166,0.00503192,0.0339802,0.0209973,0.01068291,-0.02240949,-0.01670799,-0.00012296,0.0557033,-0.04324766,-0.0425059,0.00430217,-0.01278258,-0.07085458,0.01147593,0.00037524,-0.29348364,-0.02171966,-0.02160861,0.02808598,-0.02397947,-0.00667374,0.05039707,-0.03890413,-0.10391981,-0.02586206,-0.08816733,0.09067524,0.04463389,-0.02344445,0.04869062,-0.09560627,0.06630825,-0.05503698,0.01360357,0.01027302,0.04398474,0.03112681,0.21955052,0.01133699,0.0560586,-0.00337893,0.03661321,0.02306616,0.0441542,-0.02929661,-0.00192474,-0.05100278,0.12406573,-0.06738123,0.03786947,0.01569853,-0.05904981,-0.01093167,0.05105031,0.0402314,0.01944806,0.01070402,-0.07356104,0.01405467,0.10240298,0.03987842,-0.02571002,-0.05195574,0.0263298,0.00017265,-0.01652211,0.08796053,-0.02738716,-0.0045576,-0.01410095,0.05040028,-0.04913411,0.0123392,-0.03026823,-0.05832202,-0.02985999,-0.02703127,0.02940457,0.12723675,0.04483248],"last_embed":{"hash":"fzb72v","tokens":461}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"fzb72v","at":1772710041570},"key":" 想法/想法记录/题目收集.md#题目收集##解答  (1) 求夹角 $\\theta$ 椭圆 $\\Gamma: \\frac{x^2}{3}+y^2=1$，点 $A$ 的横坐标为 $-\\frac{3}{2}$，代入椭圆方程得： $$\\frac{(-\\frac{3}{2})^2}{3} + y^2 = 1 \\implies \\frac{3}{4} + y^2 = 1 \\implies y = \\pm \\frac{1}{2}$$ 直线 $l_1$ 过 $M(0,2)$ 和 $A$，设 $l_1$ 的斜率为 $k_1$，直线与椭圆交于相异两点，故判别式 $\\Delta>0$： 联立 $y=kx+2$ 与椭圆方程，得 $\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)x^2+4kx+3=0$，$\\Delta=16k^2-4\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)\\cdot3=4k^2-4>0$，即 $|k|>1$。 - 若 $y=\\frac{1}{2}$，则 $k_1=\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=1$，$\\Delta=0$（相切，舍去）； - 若 $y=-\\frac{1}{2}$，则 $k_1=\\frac{-\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=\\frac{5}{3}$，满足 $|k|>1$。 $l_1,l_2$ 关于 $y$ 轴对称，故 $l_2$ 的斜率 $k_2=-\\frac{5}{3}$。两直线夹角公式：$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{|1+k_1k_2|}{\\sqrt{1+k_1^2}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+k_2^2}}$，代入得： $$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{\\left|1-\\frac{25}{9}\\right|}{\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}}=\\frac{\\frac{16}{9}}{\\frac{34}{9}}=\\frac{8}{17}$$ 故 $\\theta=\\arccos\\frac{8}{17}$。#{1}","lines":[6,6],"size":2282,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"fzb72v","at":1772710041570}},"smart_blocks: 想法/想法记录/题目收集.md#题目收集##解答 #### (1) 求夹角$\\theta$ 椭圆$\\Gamma: \\frac{x^2}{3}+y^2=1$，点$A$的横坐标为$-\\frac{3}{2}$，代入椭圆方程得： $$\\frac{(-\\frac{3}{2})^2}{3} + y^2 = 1 \\implies \\frac{3}{4} + y^2 = 1 \\implies y = \\pm \\frac{1}{2}$$ 直线$l_1$过$M(0,2)$和$A$，设$l_1$的斜率为$k_1$，直线与椭圆交于相异两点，故判别式$\\Delta>0$： 联立$y=kx+2$与椭圆方程，得$\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)x^2+4kx+3=0$，$\\Delta=16k^2-4\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)\\cdot3=4k^2-4>0$，即$|k|>1$。 - 若$y=\\frac{1}{2}$，则$k_1=\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=1$，$\\Delta=0$（相切，舍去）； - 若$y=-\\frac{1}{2}$，则$k_1=\\frac{-\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=\\frac{5}{3}$，满足$|k|>1$。 $l_1,l_2$关于$y$轴对称，故$l_2$的斜率$k_2=-\\frac{5}{3}$。 两直线夹角公式：$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{|1+k_1k_2|}{\\sqrt{1+k_1^2}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+k_2^2}}$，代入得： $$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{\\left|1-\\frac{25}{9}\\right|}{\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}}=\\frac{\\frac{16}{9}}{\\frac{34}{9}}=\\frac{8}{17}$$ 故$\\theta=\\arccos\\frac{8}{17}$。 #### (2) 求直线$l_2$的方程 $\\triangle MAD$与$\\triangle MAC$有公共顶点$A$，底边$MD,MC$在直线$l_2$上，故面积比等于底边长之比： $$\\frac{S_{\\triangle MAD}}{S_{\\triangle MAC}}=\\frac{|MD|}{|MC|}=2$$ 点$C$在线段$MD$上，故$|MD|=2|MC|$，即$C$为$MD$的中点，设$l_2$的方程为$y=mx+2$，联立椭圆方程得： $$\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+m^2\\right)x^2+4mx+3=0$$ 设$C(x_1,y_1),D(x_2,y_2)$，由韦达定理： $$x_1+x_2=-\\frac{12m}{1+3m^2},\\quad x_1x_2=\\frac{9}{1+3m^2}$$ 由$|MD|=2|MC|$，得$x_2=2x_1$（同方向），代入韦达定理： $$3x_1=-\\frac{12m}{1+3m^2},\\quad 2x_1^2=\\frac{9}{1+3m^2}$$ 消去$x_1$得： $$2\\cdot\\left(-\\frac{4m}{1+3m^2}\\right)^2=\\frac{9}{1+3m^2} \\implies 32m^2=9(1+3m^2) \\implies m^2=\\frac{9}{5}$$ 解得$m=\\pm\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}$，满足$\\Delta=4m^2-4>0$。 故直线$l_2$的方程为： $$y=\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}x+2 \\quad \\text{或} \\quad y=-\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}x+2$$ 整理为标准式：$3\\sqrt{5}x-5y+10=0$ 或 $3\\sqrt{5}x+5y-10=0$。 #### (3) 求$\\lambda$的取值范围 设过$M(0,2)$的直线斜率为$k$，联立椭圆方程得$\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)x^2+4kx+3=0$，设交点为$P(x_1,y_1),Q(x_2,y_2)$，则： $$\\overrightarrow{MP}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{MQ}=x_1x_2+(y_1-2)(y_2-2)=x_1x_2+k^2x_1x_2=(1+k^2)x_1x_2$$ 代入$x_1x_2=\\frac{9}{1+3k^2}$，得： $$|\\overrightarrow{MP}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{MQ}|=\\frac{9(1+k^2)}{1+3k^2}$$ 对$l_1,l_2$，有$|\\overrightarrow{AM}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{BM}|=\\frac{9(1+k_1^2)}{1+3k_1^2}$，$|\\overrightarrow{CM}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{DM}|=\\frac{9(1+k_2^2)}{1+3k_2^2}$，代入等式得： $$\\lambda=\\frac{(1+k_1^2)(1+3k_2^2)}{(1+3k_1^2)(1+k_2^2)}$$ 由直线与椭圆交于相异两点，得$k_1^2>1,k_2^2>1$。令$f(k)=\\frac{1+k^2}{1+3k^2}$，则$f(k)$在$k^2>1$时单调递减，值域为$\\left(\\frac{1}{3},\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$。 两直线夹角$\\theta\\in(0,\\frac{\\pi}{4}]$，故$\\tan\\theta=\\left|\\frac{k_2-k_1}{1+k_1k_2}\\right|\\leq1$，平方得$(k_2-k_1)^2\\leq(1+k_1k_2)^2$，整理得： $$k_1^2k_2^2 -k_1^2 -k_2^2 +4k_1k_2 +1\\geq0$$ 当$k_1^2>1,k_2^2>1$时，该式恒成立（因式分解可证两个因子均为正）。 因此$\\lambda=\\frac{f(k_1)}{f(k_2)}$，其中$f(k_1),f(k_2)\\in\\left(\\frac{1}{3},\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$，故： $$\\frac{\\frac{1}{3}}{\\frac{1}{2}} < \\lambda < \\frac{\\frac{1}{2}}{\\frac{1}{3}} \\implies \\frac{2}{3} < \\lambda < \\frac{3}{2}$$ 即$\\lambda$的取值范围为$\\left(\\frac{2}{3},\\frac{3}{2}\\right)$。 ### 最终答案 (1) $\\boldsymbol{\\theta=\\arccos\\frac{8}{17}}$ (2) 直线$l_2$的方程为$\\boldsymbol{y=\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}x+2}$ 或 $\\boldsymbol{y=-\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}x+2}$（或标准式$3\\sqrt{5}x-5y+10=0$、$3\\sqrt{5}x+5y-10=0$） (3) $\\lambda$的取值范围为$\\boldsymbol{\\left(\\frac{2}{3},\\frac{3}{2}\\right)}$": null,
"smart_blocks: 想法/想法记录/题目收集.md#题目收集##解答  (1) 求夹角 $\\theta$ 椭圆 $\\Gamma: \\frac{x^2}{3}+y^2=1$，点 $A$ 的横坐标为 $-\\frac{3}{2}$，代入椭圆方程得： $$\\frac{(-\\frac{3}{2})^2}{3} + y^2 = 1 \\implies \\frac{3}{4} + y^2 = 1 \\implies y = \\pm \\frac{1}{2}$$ 直线 $l_1$ 过 $M(0,2)$ 和 $A$，设 $l_1$ 的斜率为 $k_1$，直线与椭圆交于相异两点，故判别式 $\\Delta>0$： 联立 $y=kx+2$ 与椭圆方程，得 $\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)x^2+4kx+3=0$，$\\Delta=16k^2-4\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)\\cdot3=4k^2-4>0$，即 $|k|>1$。 - 若 $y=\\frac{1}{2}$，则 $k_1=\\frac{\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=1$，$\\Delta=0$（相切，舍去）； - 若 $y=-\\frac{1}{2}$，则 $k_1=\\frac{-\\frac{1}{2}-2}{-\\frac{3}{2}-0}=\\frac{5}{3}$，满足 $|k|>1$。 $l_1,l_2$ 关于 $y$ 轴对称，故 $l_2$ 的斜率 $k_2=-\\frac{5}{3}$。两直线夹角公式：$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{|1+k_1k_2|}{\\sqrt{1+k_1^2}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+k_2^2}}$，代入得： $$\\cos\\theta=\\frac{\\left|1-\\frac{25}{9}\\right|}{\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}\\cdot\\sqrt{1+\\frac{25}{9}}}=\\frac{\\frac{16}{9}}{\\frac{34}{9}}=\\frac{8}{17}$$ 故 $\\theta=\\arccos\\frac{8}{17}$。 #### (2) 求直线 $l_2$ 的方程 $\\triangle MAD$ 与 $\\triangle MAC$ 有公共顶点 $A$，底边 $MD,MC$ 在直线 $l_2$ 上，故面积比等于底边长之比： $$\\frac{S_{\\triangle MAD}}{S_{\\triangle MAC}}=\\frac{|MD|}{|MC|}=2$$ 点 $C$ 在线段 $MD$ 上，故 $|MD|=2|MC|$，即 $C$ 为 $MD$ 的中点，设 $l_2$ 的方程为 $y=mx+2$，联立椭圆方程得： $$\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+m^2\\right)x^2+4mx+3=0$$ 设 $C(x_1,y_1),D(x_2,y_2)$，由韦达定理： $$x_1+x_2=-\\frac{12m}{1+3m^2},\\quad x_1x_2=\\frac{9}{1+3m^2}$$ 由 $|MD|=2|MC|$，得 $x_2=2x_1$（同方向），代入韦达定理： $$3x_1=-\\frac{12m}{1+3m^2},\\quad 2x_1^2=\\frac{9}{1+3m^2}$$ 消去 $x_1$ 得： $$2\\cdot\\left(-\\frac{4m}{1+3m^2}\\right)^2=\\frac{9}{1+3m^2} \\implies 32m^2=9(1+3m^2) \\implies m^2=\\frac{9}{5}$$ 解得 $m=\\pm\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}$，满足 $\\Delta=4m^2-4>0$。故直线 $l_2$ 的方程为： $$y=\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}x+2 \\quad \\text{或} \\quad y=-\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}x+2$$ 整理为标准式：$3\\sqrt{5}x-5y+10=0$ 或 $3\\sqrt{5}x+5y-10=0$。 #### (3) 求 $\\lambda$ 的取值范围设过 $M(0,2)$ 的直线斜率为 $k$，联立椭圆方程得 $\\left(\\frac{1}{3}+k^2\\right)x^2+4kx+3=0$，设交点为 $P(x_1,y_1),Q(x_2,y_2)$，则： $$\\overrightarrow{MP}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{MQ}=x_1x_2+(y_1-2)(y_2-2)=x_1x_2+k^2x_1x_2=(1+k^2)x_1x_2$$ 代入 $x_1x_2=\\frac{9}{1+3k^2}$，得： $$|\\overrightarrow{MP}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{MQ}|=\\frac{9(1+k^2)}{1+3k^2}$$ 对 $l_1,l_2$，有 $|\\overrightarrow{AM}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{BM}|=\\frac{9(1+k_1^2)}{1+3k_1^2}$，$|\\overrightarrow{CM}\\cdot\\overrightarrow{DM}|=\\frac{9(1+k_2^2)}{1+3k_2^2}$，代入等式得： $$\\lambda=\\frac{(1+k_1^2)(1+3k_2^2)}{(1+3k_1^2)(1+k_2^2)}$$ 由直线与椭圆交于相异两点，得 $k_1^2>1,k_2^2>1$。令 $f(k)=\\frac{1+k^2}{1+3k^2}$，则 $f(k)$ 在 $k^2>1$ 时单调递减，值域为 $\\left(\\frac{1}{3},\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$。两直线夹角 $\\theta\\in(0,\\frac{\\pi}{4}]$，故 $\\tan\\theta=\\left|\\frac{k_2-k_1}{1+k_1k_2}\\right|\\leq1$，平方得 $(k_2-k_1)^2\\leq(1+k_1k_2)^2$，整理得： $$k_1^2k_2^2 -k_1^2 -k_2^2 +4k_1k_2 +1\\geq0$$ 当 $k_1^2>1,k_2^2>1$ 时，该式恒成立（因式分解可证两个因子均为正）。因此 $\\lambda=\\frac{f(k_1)}{f(k_2)}$，其中 $f(k_1),f(k_2)\\in\\left(\\frac{1}{3},\\frac{1}{2}\\right)$，故： $$\\frac{\\frac{1}{3}}{\\frac{1}{2}} < \\lambda < \\frac{\\frac{1}{2}}{\\frac{1}{3}} \\implies \\frac{2}{3} < \\lambda < \\frac{3}{2}$$ 即 $\\lambda$ 的取值范围为 $\\left(\\frac{2}{3},\\frac{3}{2}\\right)$。 ### 最终答案 (1) $\\boldsymbol{\\theta=\\arccos\\frac{8}{17}}$ (2) 直线 $l_2$ 的方程为 $\\boldsymbol{y=\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}x+2}$ 或 $\\boldsymbol{y=-\\frac{3\\sqrt{5}}{5}x+2}$（或标准式 $3\\sqrt{5}x-5y+10=0$、$3\\sqrt{5}x+5y-10=0$） (3) $\\lambda$ 的取值范围为 $\\boldsymbol{\\left(\\frac{2}{3},\\frac{3}{2}\\right)}$": null,

